OL,3,CGrandfather who 'planned suicide' says
OL,4,Ccharity helped turn life around
OL,6,FSam told ITV Granada Reports he had
OL,7,Fbegun saying goodbye to his friends
OL,8,F'in his own way' as he planned his
OL,9,Fsuicide.
OL,11,FA grandfather-of-two has revealed how
OL,12,Fhe spent weeks planning his suicide
OL,13,Fbut was brought back from the brink by
OL,14,Ffinally admitting to others how he was
OL,15,Ftruly feeling.
OL,17,FSam Samuel, 57, from Oldham, said when
OL,18,Fhe had made the decision to take his
OL,19,Fown life, his mood lifted, and he said
OL,20,Fgoodbye to his friends "in his own
OL,21,Fway".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/14
