OL,3,CGrandfather who 'planned suicide' says
OL,4,Ccharity helped turn life around
OL,6,FBut, it was a night at Andy's Man
OL,7,FClub, a therapy group where men of all
OL,8,Fages from different backgrounds, get
OL,9,Ftogether and talk about their
OL,10,Fexperiences, which was the turning
OL,11,Fpoint.
OL,13,FFor many years, Sam had struggled with
OL,14,Fdepression that went undiagnosed.
OL,16,FHe was moody, self-absorbed and "just
OL,17,Fdidn't care", but recognising the
OL,18,Fissue, Sam went to his GP: "I told him
OL,19,F'I can't cope with this. I can't cope
OL,20,Fwith feeling like this. I can't cope
OL,21,Fwith the emptiness'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/14
