OL,3,CGrandfather who 'planned suicide' says
OL,4,Ccharity helped turn life around
OL,6,F"My life was just a blur. I didn't
OL,7,Fwant to die, but I didn't want to live
OL,8,Feither."
OL,10,FSam was prescribed medication and he
OL,11,Fjoined a local branch of Andy's Man
OL,12,FClub.
OL,14,FSam said: "The mantra of Andy's Man
OL,15,FClub is 'it's okay to talk'. Talking
OL,16,Fis something that men don't do and
OL,17,Ffinding a place where you could talk
OL,18,Fso freely was thoroughly refreshing."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/14
