OL,3,CGrandfather who 'planned suicide' says
OL,4,Ccharity helped turn life around
OL,6,FBut Sam said he was just "going
OL,7,Fthrough the motions" at the meetings,
OL,8,Fas unbeknown to the rest of the group
OL,9,Fwas planning his suicide.
OL,11,F"I spent three or four weeks saying
OL,12,Fgoodbye to people in my own way. I'd
OL,13,Fplanned a time, a place, a method," he
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,F"My mood lifted straight away, once I
OL,17,Fknew that this was the path I was
OL,18,Fgoing to take, but then one Monday
OL,19,Fnight at an Andy's meeting, I was
OL,20,Fpassed the ball, which meant it was my
OL,21,Fturn to talk."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/14
