OL,3,CGrandfather who 'planned suicide' says
OL,4,Ccharity helped turn life around
OL,6,FSam continued: "Something happened, I
OL,7,Fdon't know what it was, but I looked
OL,8,Fdown at this ball. I told the guys
OL,9,Fwhat I was planning. I cried and cried
OL,10,Fand cried.
OL,12,F"The guys were absolutely magnificent,
OL,13,Fand we went from Andy's to a late-
OL,14,Fnight cafe and they stayed with me and
OL,15,Fwe talked and drank coffee after
OL,16,Fcoffee.
OL,18,F"There's a closeness that I've got
OL,19,Fwith a few of those guys that I can
OL,20,Fnever explain."
