OL,3,CGrandfather who 'planned suicide' says
OL,4,Ccharity helped turn life around
OL,6,FThis was when Sam began to get himself
OL,7,Fbetter. Initially filling his days
OL,8,Fwith his hobby of photography, he
OL,9,Freturned to work as an IT Manager for
OL,10,FOldham Council.
OL,12,FNow, he is a Mental Health First
OL,13,FAider, listening to colleagues and
OL,14,Fdelivering talks at work.
OL,16,FHe has also recently trained as a
OL,17,FSamaritans volunteer listener, and
OL,18,Fsays Andy's Man Club has become a huge
OL,19,Fpart of his life.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/14
