OL,3,CGrandfather who 'planned suicide' says
OL,4,Ccharity helped turn life around
OL,6,F"I got more and more involved and now
OL,7,FI lead the Oldham group," he said.
OL,8,F"It's so nice to be able to say, 'You
OL,9,Fknow what? I've been there mate. I've
OL,10,Fbeen there'.
OL,12,F"My life now? It couldn't be better. I
OL,13,Factually like myself now. And at 57
OL,14,Fyears old, it's taken all this time to
OL,15,Flike myself, but I do and I'm not
OL,16,Fashamed to say it."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/14
