OL,3,CGrandfather who 'planned suicide' says
OL,4,Ccharity helped turn life around
OL,6,FAndrea Newton is also sharing her
OL,7,Fstory of hope as part of Greater
OL,8,FManchester's Shining a Light on
OL,9,FSuicide campaign to raise awareness of
OL,10,Fbeing suicide bereaved and give hope
OL,11,Fto those struggling with suicidal
OL,12,Fthoughts.
OL,14,FWith her flame coloured hair and
OL,15,Foutgoing manner, Andrea said: "When
OL,16,Fpeople meet me for the first time,
OL,17,Fthey tend to think that I'm very
OL,18,Fconfident, extrovert and outgoing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/14
