OL,3,CGrandfather who 'planned suicide' says
OL,4,Ccharity helped turn life around
OL,6,F"There have been occasions where I've
OL,7,Fbeen described as a gobby Northern
OL,8,Fbird."
OL,10,FBut underneath that persona is a
OL,11,Fthoughtful and quiet woman, who at one
OL,12,Fpoint didn't want to live anymore.
OL,14,FA mother of one grown up son, who was
OL,15,Fdealing with certain circumstances in
OL,16,Flife, and also struggling with being
OL,17,Fperimenopausal, she got to a point
OL,18,Fwhere she could no longer keep up the
OL,19,Fpretence that everything was okay.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/14
