OL,3,CGrandfather who 'planned suicide' says
OL,4,Ccharity helped turn life around
OL,6,FAndrea says following a divorce she
OL,7,Fwas left with no money and ended up
OL,8,Fhomeless for three months. She said
OL,9,Fwas at rock bottom and intended to end
OL,10,Fher life to end the pain she was in.
OL,12,FWorrying what might happened to her
OL,13,Fdog if she took her own life prompted
OL,14,Fher to seek help and she called
OL,15,FSamaritans, and a kind voice at the
OL,16,Fend of the phone gave her the chance
OL,17,Fto speak about how she was really
OL,18,Ffeeling.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/14
