OL,3,CGrandfather who 'planned suicide' says
OL,4,Ccharity helped turn life around
OL,6,FAndrea explains: "That conversation
OL,7,Fwas the start of the climb back up. I
OL,8,Fmade a promise to the universe that if
OL,9,FI made it through that living hell, I
OL,10,Fwould use what I had learned to help
OL,11,Fother people.
OL,13,F"I would use my past to make other
OL,14,Fpeople's futures more positive."
OL,16,FAndrea has now qualified as a suicide
OL,17,Fintervention tutor and is working with
OL,18,Fworkplaces to help people have more
OL,19,Fconfident conversations and talk more
OL,20,Fopenly about mental health and
OL,21,Fsuicidal feelings.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/14
