OL,3,CGrandfather who 'planned suicide' says
OL,4,Ccharity helped turn life around
OL,6,FShe said: "Over the past few years
OL,7,Fthere has been a lot of coverage of
OL,8,Fmale suicide because statistically in
OL,9,Fthe UK men represent the greatest
OL,10,Fnumber of deaths by suicide.
OL,12,F"However, what we don't count and what
OL,13,Fwe don't have statistics for, is the
OL,14,Fnumber of women who attempt, and what
OL,15,Fwe know is twice as many women will
OL,16,Fattempt suicide.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/14
