OL,3,CGrandfather who 'planned suicide' says
OL,4,Ccharity helped turn life around
OL,6,F"I know that Granada has given
OL,7,Fcoverage to the Three Dads Walking,
OL,8,Fwhere their three young daughters took
OL,9,Ftheir own lives, and it's really
OL,10,Fimportant that we recognise that women
OL,11,Fare as much at risk as men.
OL,13,F"The most significant rise in recent
OL,14,Ftimes has been young women.
OL,16,F"We're also learning a lot more about
OL,17,Fthe menopause and the impact that
OL,18,Fhormones can have, and actually, for a
OL,19,Fperimenopausal woman the risk of
OL,20,Fsuicidal thoughts can increase by a
OL,21,Ffactor of seven.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/14
